{"id":631894423,"lang":"java","time":"6 months, 1 week","timestamp":1643673181,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/631894423/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Add Two Numbers","memory":"47.5 MB","code":"/**\n * Definition for singly-linked list.\n * public class ListNode {\n *     int val;\n *     ListNode next;\n *     ListNode() {}\n *     ListNode(int val) { this.val = val; }\n *     ListNode(int val, ListNode next) { this.val = val; this.next = next; }\n * }\n */\nclass Solution {\n    public ListNode addTwoNumbers(ListNode l1, ListNode l2) {\n        ListNode head = new ListNode();\n        ListNode walk = head;\n        \n        int remainder = 0;\n        while(l1 != null && l2 != null) {\n            int sum = l1.val + l2.val + remainder;\n            remainder = sum / 10;\n            sum = sum % 10;\n            ListNode current = new ListNode(sum, null);\n            walk.next = current;\n            walk = current;\n            l1 = l1.next;\n            l2 = l2.next;\n        }\n        while(l1 != null) {\n            int sum = l1.val + remainder;\n            remainder = sum / 10;\n            sum = sum % 10;\n            ListNode current = new ListNode(sum, null);\n            walk.next = current;\n            walk = current;\n            l1 = l1.next;\n        }\n        while(l2 != null) {\n            int sum = l2.val + remainder;\n            remainder = sum / 10;\n            sum = sum % 10;\n            ListNode current = new ListNode(sum, null);\n            walk.next = current;\n            walk = current;\n            l2 = l2.next;\n        }\n        if(remainder != 0) {\n            ListNode current = new ListNode(remainder, null);\n            walk.next = current;\n            walk = current;\n        }\n        return head.next;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"add-two-numbers"}
